title: Amateur Badminton Tournament
note: Come join us for our first amateur badminton tournament at The Courtside Club in Westborough, MA on April 21st at 1:00pm. Put your skills to the test, meet new players, and have a chance to win prizes!

title: Weekend Badminton Social
note: Join us for a fun and social badminton morning at the Atlanta Badminton Club in Norcross, GA on May 13th at 10:00am. We'll be playing doubles matches and enjoying some snacks and refreshments afterwards. All skill levels welcome!

title: Beginner's Badminton Workshop
note: Learn the basics of badminton and improve your game at our beginner's workshop at Badminton Alley in El Monte, CA on June 1st at 7:00pm. Our experienced coaches will guide you through the fundamentals of badminton, from grip and footwork to serves and clears. Rackets provided.
